74
00:06:23,450 --> 00:06:24,090
What is it?

75
00:06:24,090 --> 00:06:24,710
Give it to me!

76
00:06:24,930 --> 00:06:25,570
What's this?

77
00:06:31,890 --> 00:06:32,530
