78
00:06:36,650 --> 00:06:37,370
What is it!

79
00:06:39,330 --> 00:06:40,410
Enough, enough, give it to me!

80
00:06:40,970 --> 00:06:41,730
Give it over, give it now!

81
00:06:41,730 --> 00:06:42,730
